.Dd August 2, 2018
.Dt RC.SHUTDOWN 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm rc.shutdown
.Nd executed by init during shutdown
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm rc.shutdown
script is responsible for killing all LeanInit services and
unmounting all file systems before init calls
.Nm reboot(2).

